{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876485794,"sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7cad0c001deqDKyExdST5c2","messageID":"msg_d7a7c970e001WrxLxhx7AdJJcB","sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_d1fe61e73bd84623ae30d5d4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 建立完整的 Makefile 构建目标体系，支持 Go 源码编译、Docker 镜像构建、测试运行、代码检查等开发全生命周期操作，统一入口简化开发者体验。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: ### Background\n12: \n13: AgentCube 项目当前 Makefile 仅包含 Docker 镜像构建目标（AR-032），缺少：\n14: - Go 源码直接编译目标（跨平台二进制）\n15: - 测试执行目标\n16: - 代码检查/格式化目标\n17: - 开发工作流集成目标\n18: \n19: 开发者需要记忆多个独立命令（如 `go build`, `go test`, `golangci-lint`），缺乏统一入口。\n20: \n21: ### Goal\n22: \n23: 扩展 Makefile 为完整的构建工具链：\n24: - 支持 Go 二进制直接编译（支持多平台交叉编译）\n25: - 集成测试、lint、format 等开发工具\n26: - 提供开发/测试/发布等分层工作流\n27: - 与现有 Docker 目标无缝集成\n28: \n29: ### Value\n30: \n31: - **一致性**：所有构建操作通过 `make` 统一入口\n32: - **效率**：常用工作流一键完成（如 `make dev` 启动开发环境）\n33: - **可发现性**：`make help` 显示所有可用目标\n34: - **跨平台**：支持 Linux/Darwin/Windows，交叉编译多架构\n35: - **CI 集成**：便于流水线调用统一构建命令\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## Scope\n40: \n41: ### In-Scope\n42: \n43: | Target Category | Targets | Description |\n44: |-----------------|---------|-------------|\n45: | Binary Build | `build`, `build-router`, `build-workload-manager`, `build-agentd`, `build-picod` | 编译 Go 源码为二进制 |\n46: | Cross-compile | `build-linux-amd64`, `build-linux-arm64`, `build-darwin-amd64`, `build-darwin-arm64` | 跨平台编译 |\n47: | Docker Build | `docker-build`, `docker-build-*` | Docker 镜像构建（现有） |\n48: | Testing | `test`, `test-unit`, `test-integration`, `test-cover` | 运行单元/集成测试 |\n49: | Linting | `lint`, `lint-fix`, `fmt` | 代码检查与格式化 |\n50: | Development | `dev`, `dev-docker`, `watch` | 开发环境启动 |\n51: | Cleanup | `clean`, `docker-clean` | 清理构建产物 |\n52: | Utilities | `help`, `version`, `deps` | 帮助/版本/依赖管理 |\n53: \n54: ### Out-of-Scope\n55: \n56: - CI/CD 流水线配置（独立 AR）\n57: - Helm chart 相关目标（AR-030）\n58: - 发布版本自动化（独立流程）\n59: - 本地 Kubernetes 集群管理\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## Impact Analysis\n64: \n65: ### Dependencies\n66: \n67: | Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n68: |------------|---------|--------|\n69: | Go 1.24+ | 源码编译 | 项目已使用 |\n70: | golangci-lint | 代码检查 | 需引入 |\n71: | gofmt/goimports | 代码格式化 | 标准工具 |\n72: | Docker | 镜像构建 | 已有 |\n73: | kind/kubectl | 本地开发环境 | 外部依赖 |\n74: \n75: ### Upstream\n76: \n77: - `cmd/router/` — Router 源码\n78: - `cmd/workload-manager/` — Workload Manager 源码\n79: - `cmd/agentd/` — Agentd 源码\n80: - `cmd/picod/` — Picod 源码\n81: - `go.mod` / `go.sum` — Go 依赖\n82: \n83: ### Downstream Consumers\n84: \n85: 1. **开发者** — 本地构建、测试、开发\n86: 2. **CI/CD** — 流水线调用统一构建命令\n87: 3. **AR-032** — Docker 构建依赖此 Makefile 扩展\n88: \n89: ### Risks\n90: \n91: | Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n92: |------|----------|------------|\n93: | Makefile 过于复杂 | Medium | 按分类组织，保持简洁，优先常用目标 |\n94: | 跨平台兼容 | Medium | 使用 Go 跨平台特性，避免 shell 依赖 |\n95: | 依赖缺失 | Low | 目标添加依赖检查，友好报错 |\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ## Alternatives Considered\n100: \n101: ### Option 1: 保持现状，仅用 Docker 目标（Not Selected）\n102: \n103: **Pros**: 简单，现有目标已满足 Docker 需求\n104: **Cons**: 开发者需单独学习 Go 构建命令，无统一入口\n105: \n106: ### Option 2: 仅添加 Go 编译目标（Not Selected）\n107: \n108: **Pros**: 满足编译需求，简单\n109: **Cons**: 缺少测试、lint 等开发必需功能\n110: \n111: ### Option 3: 完整 Makefile 目标体系（Selected）\n112: \n113: **Pros**: 统一入口，功能完整，符合行业最佳实践\n114: **Cons**: 初始实现工作量较大\n115: \n116: ### Option 4: 使用 goreleaser 或其他工具（Not Selected）\n117: \n118: **Pros**: 功能强大，支持发布\n119: **Cons**: 过度设计，开发阶段不需要；增加外部依赖\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ## Technical Design\n124: \n125: ### 目标层级结构\n126: \n127: ```\n128: Makefile\n129: ├── 基础变量 (DOCKER_REGISTRY, GO_VERSION, BINARY_VERSION 等)\n130: ├── 帮助信息 (通过 self-documenting makefile)\n131: │\n132: ├── build (默认)\n133: │   ├── build-router\n134: │   ├── build-workload-manager\n135: │   ├── build-agentd\n136: │   └── build-picod\n137: │\n138: ├── cross-build (交叉编译)\n139: │   ├── build-linux-amd64\n140: │   ├── build-linux-arm64\n141: │   ├── build-darwin-amd64\n142: │   └── build-darwin-arm64\n143: │\n144: ├── docker-* (Docker 相关)\n145: │   └── 现有目标...\n146: │\n147: ├── test\n148: │   ├── test-unit\n149: │   ├── test-integration\n150: │   └── test-cover\n151: │\n152: ├── lint & fmt\n153: │\n154: ├── dev\n155: │   ├── dev-docker\n156: │   └── dev-kind\n157: │\n158: └── clean & help\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ### 核心目标实现\n162: \n163: #### Binary Build\n164: \n165: ```makefile\n166: # 构建变量\n167: BINARIES := router workload-manager agentd picod\n168: GO_LDFLAGS := -s -w -X main.version=$(BINARY_VERSION)\n169: \n170: # 主构建目标\n171: .PHONY: build\n172: build: $(BINARIES)\n173: \n174: router:\n175: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/router ./cmd/router\n176: \n177: workload-manager:\n178: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/workload-manager ./cmd/workload-manager\n179: \n180: agentd:\n181: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/agentd ./cmd/agentd\n182: \n183: picod:\n184: \tCGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -ldflags=\"$(GO_LDFLAGS)\" -o bin/picod ./cmd/picod\n185: ```\n186: \n187: #### Cross-compile\n188: \n189: ```makefile\n190: .PHONY: cross-build\n191: cross-build: build-linux-amd64 build-linux-arm64 build-darwin-amd64 build-darwin-arm64\n192: \n193: build-linux-amd64:\n194: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -o bin/linux-amd64/router ./cmd/router\n195: \t# ... 其他二进制\n196: \n197: build-linux-arm64:\n198: \tGOOS=linux GOARCH=arm64 go build -o bin/linux-arm64/router ./cmd/router\n199: \t# ... 其他二进制\n200: # 类似 darwin 目标\n201: ```\n202: \n203: #### Test\n204: \n205: ```makefile\n206: .PHONY: test test-unit test-integration test-cover\n207: test: test-unit\n208: \n209: test-unit:\n210: \tgo test -v -short ./...\n211: \n212: test-integration:\n213: \tgo test -v -tags=integration ./integration/...\n214: \n215: test-cover:\n216: \tgo test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./...\n217: \tgo tool cover -html=coverage.out -o coverage.html\n218: ```\n219: \n220: #### Lint & Format\n221: \n222: ```makefile\n223: .PHONY: lint lint-fix fmt\n224: \n225: lint:\n226: \tgolangci-lint run ./...\n227: \n228: lint-fix:\n229: \tgolangci-lint run --fix ./...\n230: \n231: fmt:\n232: \tgofmt -w -s .\n233: \tgoimports -w .\n234: ```\n235: \n236: #### Development\n237: \n238: ```makefile\n239: .PHONY: dev dev-docker\n240: dev: dev-docker\n241: \n242: dev-docker:\n243: \tdocker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d\n244: \n245: dev-kind:\n246: \tkind create cluster --name agentcube\n247: \tkubectl apply -f manifests/\n248: ```\n249: \n250: #### Help (Self-documenting)\n251: \n252: ```makefile\n253: .PHONY: help\n254: help:\n255: \t@echo \"AgentCube Makefile Targets\"\n256: \t@echo \"\"\n257: \t@echo \"Build:\"\n258: \t@echo \"  make build              # Build all binaries for current platform\"\n259: \t@echo \"  make build-<binary>     # Build specific binary (router|workload-manager|agentd|picod)\"\n260: \t@echo \"  make cross-build        # Build for all platforms\"\n261: \t@echo \"\"\n262: \t@echo \"Docker:\"\n263: \t@echo \"  make docker-build       # Build all Docker images\"\n264: \t@echo \"  make docker-push        # Push images to registry\"\n265: \t@echo \"\"\n266: \t@echo \"Test:\"\n267: \t@echo \"  make test               # Run unit tests\"\n268: \t@echo \"  make test-cover         # Run tests with coverage\"\n269: \t@echo \"\"\n270: \t@echo \"Code Quality:\"\n271: \t@echo \"  make lint               # Run linter\"\n272: \t@echo \"  make fmt                # Format code\"\n273: \t@echo \"\"\n274: \t@echo \"Development:\"\n275: \t@echo \"  make dev                # Start development environment\"\n276: \t@echo \"\"\n277: \t@echo \"Utilities:\"\n278: \t@echo \"  make clean              # Clean build artifacts\"\n279: \t@echo \"  make help               # Show this help\"\n280: ```\n281: \n282: ---\n283: \n284: ## Implementation Plan\n285: \n286: ### Phase 1: 扩展基础构建目标\n287: \n288: - [ ] 扩展 `build` 目标支持所有二进制\n289: - [ ] 添加 `build-<binary>` 独立目标\n290: - [ ] 添加跨平台编译目标\n291: \n292: ### Phase 2: 测试与代码质量\n293: \n294: - [ ] 添加 `test`, `test-unit`, `test-cover` 目标\n295: - [ ] 添加 `lint`, `fmt` 目标\n296: - [ ] 配置 golangci-lint config\n297: \n298: ### Phase 3: 开发工作流\n299: \n300: - [ ] 添加 `dev`, `dev-docker` 目标\n301: - [ ] 添加 `watch` 文件监控目标（可选）\n302: \n303: ### Phase 4: 工具与文档\n304: \n305: - [ ] 添加 `help` 自文档目标\n306: - [ ] 添加 `deps` 依赖检查目标\n307: - [ ] 验证所有目标可执行\n308: \n309: ---\n310: \n311: ## Acceptance Criteria\n312: \n313: | ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n314: |----|----------|-----------------|\n315: | MAKE-001 | 执行 `make build` | 成功编译 router, workload-manager, agentd, picod 到 bin/ 目录 |\n316: | MAKE-002 | 执行 `make build-router` | 仅编译 router 二进制 |\n317: | MAKE-003 | 执行 `make cross-build` | 生成多平台多架构二进制 |\n318: | MAKE-004 | 执行 `make test` | 运行单元测试并报告结果 |\n319: | MAKE-005 | 执行 `make lint` | 运行 golangci-lint 检查代码 |\n320: | MAKE-006 | 执行 `make fmt` | 格式化代码 |\n321: | MAKE-007 | 执行 `make help` | 显示所有可用目标及说明 |\n322: | MAKE-008 | 执行 `make clean` | 清理 bin/、coverage.out 等构建产物 |\n323: | MAKE-009 | Docker 目标仍正常工作 | `make docker-build` 功能不受影响 |\n324: \n325: ---\n326: \n327: ## Relationship to Other ARs\n328: \n329: - **AR-032** — Docker 多阶段构建依赖此 Makefile 的扩展目标\n330: - **AR-030** — Helm chart 部署不受影响\n331: - 独立 AR — CI/CD 流水线将调用 `make` 目标\n332: \n333: ---\n334: \n335: ## Timeline Estimate\n336: \n337: | Phase | Effort |\n338: |-------|--------|\n339: | 基础构建目标 | 1 小时 |\n340: | 测试与代码质量 | 1.5 小时 |\n341: | 开发工作流 | 1 小时 |\n342: | 工具与文档 | 30 分钟 |\n343: | 验证与调试 | 1 小时 |\n344: | **Total** | **5 小时** |\n\n(End of file - total 344 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Summary\n\n建立完整的 Makefile 构建目标体系，支持 Go 源码编译、Docker 镜像构建、测试运行、代码检查等开发全生命周期操作，统一入口简化开发者体验。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nAgentCube 项目当前 Makefile 仅包含 Docker 镜像构建目标（AR-032），缺少：\n- Go 源码直接编译目标（跨平台二进制）\n- 测试执行目标\n- 代码检查/格式化目标\n- 开发工作流集成目标\n\n开发者需要记忆多个独立命令（如 `go build`, `go test`, `golangci-lint`），缺乏统一入口。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775876485768,"end":1775876485791}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775876485821,"sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7cb2a1001RayTqmMYxNC2Sx","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a7c970e001WrxLxhx7AdJJcB","sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":18236,"input":3251,"output":144,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":14841}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775876489186,"sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7cbfe0001kDJ0FOn5MiAccE","messageID":"msg_d7a7cb2d8001spWQODVzHiUVbi","sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876491908,"sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7cc424001CXQagGuzEhX8GM","messageID":"msg_d7a7cb2d8001spWQODVzHiUVbi","sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_3612be532cbc49f48ea750e0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing a comprehensive Makefile build target system for AgentCube, supporting Go source compilation, Docker image building, testing, linting, and development workflows.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-033\n10: - **Module**: `root`\n11: - **Language**: `Makefile`\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Scenario: Binary Build Targets\n17: \n18: ### AR-033-001: Build all binaries\n19: \n20: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root with Go source code\n21: - **WHEN** running `make build`\n22: - **THEN** it SHALL compile router, workload-manager, agentd, and picod binaries\n23: - **AND** SHALL place them in `bin/` directory\n24: - **AND** SHALL use CGO_ENABLED=0 for static linking\n25: - **AND** SHALL inject version via ldflags (-X main.version=$(BINARY_VERSION))\n26: \n27: ### AR-033-002: Build individual binary - router\n28: \n29: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n30: - **WHEN** running `make build-router`\n31: - **THEN** it SHALL compile only router binary\n32: - **AND** SHALL place it at `bin/router`\n33: \n34: ### AR-033-003: Build individual binary - workload-manager\n35: \n36: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n37: - **WHEN** running `make build-workload-manager`\n38: - **THEN** it SHALL compile only workload-manager binary\n39: - **AND** SHALL place it at `bin/workload-manager`\n40: \n41: ### AR-033-004: Build individual binary - agentd\n42: \n43: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n44: - **WHEN** running `make build-agentd`\n45: - **THEN** it SHALL compile only agentd binary\n46: - **AND** SHALL place it at `bin/agentd`\n47: \n48: ### AR-033-005: Build individual binary - picod\n49: \n50: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n51: - **WHEN** running `make build-picod`\n52: - **THEN** it SHALL compile only picod binary\n53: - **AND** SHALL place it at `bin/picod`\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## Scenario: Cross-Compilation Targets\n58: \n59: ### AR-033-006: Build for Linux amd64\n60: \n61: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n62: - **WHEN** running `make build-linux-amd64`\n63: - **THEN** it SHALL compile all binaries for linux/amd64\n64: - **AND** SHALL place them in `bin/linux-amd64/` directory\n65: \n66: ### AR-033-007: Build for Linux arm64\n67: \n68: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n69: - **WHEN** running `make build-linux-arm64`\n70: - **THEN** it SHALL compile all binaries for linux/arm64\n71: - **AND** SHALL place them in `bin/linux-arm64/` directory\n72: \n73: ### AR-033-008: Build for Darwin amd64\n74: \n75: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n76: - **WHEN** running `make build-darwin-amd64`\n77: - **THEN** it SHALL compile all binaries for darwin/amd64\n78: - **AND** SHALL place them in `bin/darwin-amd64/` directory\n79: \n80: ### AR-033-009: Build for Darwin arm64\n81: \n82: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n83: - **WHEN** running `make build-darwin-arm64`\n84: - **THEN** it SHALL compile all binaries for darwin/arm64\n85: - **AND** SHALL place them in `bin/darwin-arm64/` directory\n86: \n87: ### AR-033-010: Cross-build all platforms\n88: \n89: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n90: - **WHEN** running `make cross-build`\n91: - **THEN** it SHALL execute all cross-compilation targets\n92: - **AND** SHALL produce binaries for linux-amd64, linux-arm64, darwin-amd64, darwin-arm64\n93: \n94: ---\n95: \n96: ## Scenario: Docker Build Integration\n97: \n98: ### AR-033-011: Docker build all images\n99: \n100: - **GIVEN** Makefile with docker targets\n101: - **WHEN** running `make docker-build`\n102: - **THEN** it SHALL build router, workload-manager, and agentd images\n103: - **AND** SHALL tag each with :latest tag (unchanged from AR-032)\n104: \n105: ### AR-033-012: Docker build individual image - router\n106: \n107: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n108: - **WHEN** running `make docker-build-router`\n109: - **THEN** it SHALL build only router image\n110: - **AND** SHALL tag as agentcube-router:latest\n111: \n112: ### AR-033-013: Docker build individual image - workload-manager\n113: \n114: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n115: - **WHEN** running `make docker-build-workload-manager`\n116: - **THEN** it SHALL build only workload-manager image\n117: - **AND** SHALL tag as agentcube-workload-manager:latest\n118: \n119: ### AR-033-014: Docker build individual image - agentd\n120: \n121: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n122: - **WHEN** running `make docker-build-agentd`\n123: - **THEN** it SHALL build only agentd image\n124: - **AND** SHALL tag as agentcube-agentd:latest\n125: \n126: ### AR-033-015: Docker push all images\n127: \n128: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n129: - **WHEN** running `make docker-push`\n130: - **THEN** it SHALL push all 3 images to registry\n131: - **AND** SHALL push both versioned and latest tags\n132: \n133: ---\n134: \n135: ## Scenario: Testing Targets\n136: \n137: ### AR-033-016: Run all tests\n138: \n139: - **GIVEN** agentcube project with test files\n140: - **WHEN** running `make test`\n141: - **THEN** it SHALL execute unit tests\n142: - **AND** SHALL use `-short` flag to skip long-running tests\n143: - **AND** SHALL display test results verbosely\n144: \n145: ### AR-033-017: Run unit tests only\n146: \n147: - **GIVEN** agentcube project\n148: - **WHEN** running `make test-unit`\n149: - **THEN** it SHALL run only unit tests\n150: - **AND** SHALL skip integration tests\n151: - **AND** SHALL use `-v` for verbose output\n152: \n153: ### AR-033-018: Run tests with coverage\n154: \n155: - **GIVEN** agentcube project\n156: - **WHEN** running `make test-cover`\n157: - **THEN** it SHALL generate coverage profile (coverage.out)\n158: - **AND** SHALL generate HTML coverage report (coverage.html)\n159: - **AND** SHALL display coverage percentage\n160: \n161: ---\n162: \n163: ## Scenario: Code Quality Targets\n164: \n165: ### AR-033-019: Run linter\n166: \n167: - **GIVEN** agentcube project with golangci-lint config\n168: - **WHEN** running `make lint`\n169: - **THEN** it SHALL execute golangci-lint on all packages\n170: - **AND** SHALL report any linting issues\n171: - **AND** SHALL exit with non-zero code if errors found\n172: \n173: ### AR-033-020: Run linter with auto-fix\n174: \n175: - **GIVEN** agentcube project\n176: - **WHEN** running `make lint-fix`\n177: - **THEN** it SHALL run golangci-lint with --fix flag\n178: - **AND** SHALL automatically fix fixable issues\n179: - **AND** SHALL report any unfixable issues\n180: \n181: ### AR-033-021: Format code\n182: \n183: - **GIVEN** agentcube project\n184: - **WHEN** running `make fmt`\n185: - **THEN** it SHALL run gofmt on all Go files\n186: - **AND** SHALL run goimports to fix imports\n187: - **AND** SHALL write changes in-place (-w flag)\n188: \n189: ---\n190: \n191: ## Scenario: Development Workflow Targets\n192: \n193: ### AR-033-022: Start development environment\n194: \n195: - **GIVEN** agentcube project with docker-compose.dev.yml\n196: - **WHEN** running `make dev`\n197: - **THEN** it SHALL start development environment via docker-compose\n198: - **AND** SHALL run in detached mode\n199: \n200: ### AR-033-023: Start development with Docker\n201: \n202: - **GIVEN** agentcube project\n203: - **WHEN** running `make dev-docker`\n204: - **THEN** it SHALL execute `docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d`\n205: - **AND** SHALL start all required services\n206: \n207: ---\n208: \n209: ## Scenario: Cleanup Targets\n210: \n211: ### AR-033-024: Clean build artifacts\n212: \n213: - **GIVEN** agentcube project with built binaries\n214: - **WHEN** running `make clean`\n215: - **THEN** it SHALL remove `bin/` directory\n216: - **AND** SHALL remove coverage files (coverage.out, coverage.html)\n217: - **AND** SHALL remove any other build artifacts\n218: \n219: ### AR-033-025: Clean Docker images\n220: \n221: - **GIVEN** built Docker images\n222: - **WHEN** running `make docker-clean`\n223: - **THEN** it SHALL remove router, workload-manager, and agentd images\n224: - **AND** SHALL handle missing images gracefully (no error if not found)\n225: \n226: ---\n227: \n228: ## Scenario: Utility Targets\n229: \n230: ### AR-033-026: Display help\n231: \n232: - **GIVEN** Makefile with help target\n233: - **WHEN** running `make help`\n234: - **THEN** it SHALL display all available targets\n235: - **AND** SHALL show categorized help text\n236: - **AND** SHALL include descriptions for each target category\n237: \n238: ### AR-033-027: Display version\n239: \n240: - **GIVEN** Makefile with version target\n241: - **WHEN** running `make version`\n242: - **THEN** it SHALL display current build version\n243: - **AND** SHALL show BINARY_VERSION variable value\n244: \n245: ### AR-033-028: Check dependencies\n246: \n247: - **GIVEN** agentcube project\n248: - **WHEN** running `make deps`\n249: - **THEN** it SHALL verify Go is installed\n250: - **AND** SHALL verify Docker is installed\n251: - **AND** SHALL verify golangci-lint is installed (optional)\n252: - **AND** SHALL display helpful error message if any dependency is missing\n253: \n254: ---\n255: \n256: ## Scenario: Variable Configuration\n257: \n258: ### AR-033-029: Docker registry configuration\n259: \n260: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n261: - **WHEN** running make with DOCKER_REGISTRY=<custom>\n262: - **THEN** it SHALL use custom registry prefix for image tags\n263: - **AND** default value SHALL be \"agentcube\"\n264: \n265: ### AR-033-030: Docker tag configuration\n266: \n267: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n268: - **WHEN** running make with DOCKER_TAG=<version>\n269: - **THEN** it SHALL use custom tag for images\n270: - **AND** default value SHALL be \"latest\"\n271: \n272: ### AR-033-031: Binary version configuration\n273: \n274: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n275: - **WHEN** running make with BINARY_VERSION=<version>\n276: - **THEN** it SHALL inject version into binary via ldflags\n277: - **AND** default value SHALL be \"dev\"\n278: \n279: ### AR-033-032: Go version configuration\n280: \n281: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n282: - **WHEN** running make with GO_VERSION=<version>\n283: - **THEN** it SHALL use specified Go version for Docker builds\n284: - **AND** default value SHALL be \"1.24\"\n285: \n286: ---\n287: \n288: ## Scenario: Default Target\n289: \n290: ### AR-033-033: Default build target\n291: \n292: - **GIVEN** agentcube project root\n293: - **WHEN** running `make` without arguments\n294: - **THEN** it SHALL execute `make build` by default\n295: - **AND** SHALL compile all binaries for current platform\n296: \n297: ---\n298: \n299: ## Scenario: Error Handling\n300: \n301: ### AR-033-034: Missing Go installation\n302: \n303: - **GIVEN** environment without Go installed\n304: - **WHEN** running any build target\n305: - **THEN** it SHALL display clear error message\n306: - **AND** SHALL indicate Go is required\n307: \n308: ### AR-033-035: Missing source code\n309: \n310: - **GIVEN** agentcube project missing cmd/ directories\n311: - **WHEN** running build target\n312: - **THEN** it SHALL fail with appropriate error from go build\n313: - **AND** SHALL not produce misleading error messages\n314: \n315: ---\n316: \n317: ## Scenario: Makefile Structure\n318: \n319: ### AR-033-036: Self-documenting makefile\n320: \n321: - **GIVEN** Makefile\n322: - **WHEN** examining makefile source\n323: - **THEN** it SHALL be organized in logical sections with comments\n324: - **AND** SHALL use .PHONY declarations for all non-file targets\n325: - **AND** SHALL define variables at the top for easy configuration\n326: \n327: ### AR-033-037: Platform-independent targets\n328: \n329: - **GIVEN** Makefile targets\n330: - **WHEN** running on Linux, macOS, or Windows\n331: - **THEN** targets SHALL execute correctly\n332: - **AND** SHALL avoid shell-specific commands\n333: \n334: ---\n335: \n336: ## References\n337: \n338: - AgentCube proposal: `changes/AR-033/proposal.md`\n339: - Existing Makefile: `Makefile`\n340: - AR-032: Dockerfile multi-stage builds (downstream consumer)\n341: - Go cross-compilation: https://go.dev/doc/install/source#environment\n342: - golangci-lint: https://golangci-lint.run/\n343: \n344: (End of file - total 311 lines)\n\n(End of file - total 344 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing a comprehensive Makefile build target system for AgentCube, supporting Go source compilation, Docker image building, testing, linting, and development workflows.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-033\n- **Module**: `root`\n- **Language**: `Makefile`\n- **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Binary Build Targets\n\n### AR-033-001: Build all binaries\n\n- **GIVEN** agentcube project root with Go source code","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775876491889,"end":1775876491905}}}}
