{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876541587,"sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7d6a64001tSdKsuCBn1cvAN","messageID":"msg_d7a7d5b73001zIEKWuLnnktgzV","sessionID":"ses_2858383fcffe3YnW7o1JN7QJzX","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_1f517713d18e432d9430754b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Design: AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n## Overview\n\n[TODO: High-level design overview]\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Workflow Directory Structure\n\n```\n.github/\n└── workflows/\n    ├── ci/\n    │   ├── build.yml\n    │   ├── test.yml\n    │   ├── lint.yml\n    │   └── security.yml\n    ├── cd/\n    │   ├── deploy-staging.yml\n    │   ├── deploy-production.yml\n    │   └── publish.yml\n    └── utils/\n        ├── triage.yml\n        ├── update-changelog.yml\n        └── sync.yml\n```\n\n### Workflow Design Patterns\n\n#### Common Patterns\n\n- **Trigger patterns**: Event-based (push, PR, schedule, manual)\n- **Job orchestration**: Sequential vs parallel execution\n- **Artifact management**: Build artifacts, test reports\n- **Secret management**: GitHub Secrets integration\n- **Matrix strategies**: Multi-version/multi-platform testing\n\n#### Shared Configuration\n\n[TODO: Define reusable workflows and composite actions]\n\n## Implementation Details\n\n### Workflow 1: TBD\n\n```yaml\n# TBD\n```\n\n---\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n- Secret rotation strategy\n- Permission least privilege\n- OIDC token usage\n- Environment protection rules\n\n---\n\n## Performance Optimization\n\n- Caching strategies\n- Parallel job execution\n- Skipping redundant runs\n\n---\n\n## Monitoring & Observability\n\n- Workflow run metrics\n- Failure alerting\n- Duration tracking\n\n(End of file)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-034/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/w